Generic single-database configuration.
first install alembic
--> pip install alembic
then make all those neccessary directory by this command
--> alembic init alembic
Then go to alembic.ini file in env/
and replace the default url with your own database url
--> sqlalchemy.url = sqlite:///./Students.db
then in env.py make these changes
-->  from database import Base and all models
-->target_metadata = Base.metadata

